SUMMARY:Kickstart Your Voice with Roanoke Talk-of-the-Town Toastmasters
DESCRIPTION:Southwest VA Toastmasters of Roanoke/Blacksburg/Rocky Mount\nTalk of the Town is Roanoke's only club that meets in the morning. Join us for a lively and supportive meeting to start your day right. We begin at 8:30 a.m. sharp. Meetings run about an hour.\n\nJoin us the 1st and 3rd Fridays of the month. We are currently meeting in person and offer Zoom\, if needed. We meet at Universal Health Corp\, 130 Church Ave SW\, Roanoke\, VA.\n\nOur Interactive meetings are designed to help you learn speaking and leadership skills and loads of interactive fun. You'll have many opportuntities to practice speaking\, hone your leadership skills and play a role in every meeting.\n\nCall or text Andree Brooks at 540-556-4432 for more information or to ensure we can be prepared with a warm welcome when you attend a meeting as a guest.
