SUMMARY:Overcome Public Speaking Fears with the Roanoke Toastmasters
DESCRIPTION:Southwest VA Toastmasters of Roanoke/Blacksburg/Rocky Mount\nWe're proud to be Roanoke Toastmasters! We are the oldest club in the area and have several active Distinguished Toastmasters (DTMs) among us. Some of our members have won competitions at the national level\, and one was recently asked to present to the International Toastmasters Conference held in Japan. We also pride ourselves on being highly supportive. Our meetings\, while formal in structure\, have a relaxed\, friendly atmosphere. We learn together\, we laugh together\, and we support each other through the journey of seeking and attaining success in furthering our professional development.\n**We welcome you to come to any of our club's meetings to learn what Toastmasters is all about.** Get a first-hand experience of how Roanoke Toastmasters can help you fine-tune\, develop or even kick-start your speaking and leadership skills. Simply sit back and get a taste of what we're about!\n\n**Advantages:**\n\n* You can overcome your fear of public speaking and hear how others have overcome theirs\n* Already a good speaker? We know you can be better. We also improve our members' ability to lead and participate in successful\, productive meetings\n* Learn to give your presentations that polished\, professional pizzazz\, and learn to gauge and hold the interest level of your audience throughout\n* Learn to think quickly on your feet!\n* You'll enjoy personal and professional benefits\n\nContact the Roanoke Toastmasters at https://bit.ly/3ZWTKxC for more information.
